text:
Great prices with free delievery!,you can't really go wrong.
i've ordered mainly blu rays,and thay have come nicely packaged and clean,one thing i will point out that the delievery could be a liitle more swifter,but thats by the by.
Overall i would highly recommend and have informed my friends and family about music magpie.
